          I am walking down the hall towards the meeting room with the old=
er lady...I don't remember her name. We are talking and as her voice trails=
 off you hear a female voice say "Guys No". 
           Now bear in mind th=
is is a class B EVP not as good as the others. It may not even say what I t=
hink it said.....but.
            That older lady and I had just walked awa=
y from Gel,Steph and Elissa and Jason, who had all just walked out on the p=
atio to confront the "lady" who was seen sitting outside. Is it possible th=

 be left alone?
                       Larry
          p.s. turn out the li=
ghts for this one...... ;)
           Last evp....no others, sorry.
